Package: promptulus
Title: AI Prompting Learning Game
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Promptulus", "Team", email = "dev@promptulus.local", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An interactive chatbot that teaches users how to write better AI
    prompts using a playful Genie personality that misinterprets prompts and
    a helpful Prompt Coach that provides constructive feedback.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
